=== OSX ===

eval `brew --config | grep HOMEBREW_PREFIX | sed 's/: /=/'`
sudo bash -c 'echo '$HOMEBREW_PREFIX/share/aclocal' >> `aclocal --print-ac-dir`/dirlist'

// http://code.google.com/p/snappy/issues/detail?id=24#c20


=== Linux ===

if there's no reaction to window resizing -> try to upgrade system libsdl and rebuild dv.

resize works ok with libsdl-1.2.15-r1 on Gentoo.

// http://bugzilla.libsdl.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1430
